Optional Prompt 3 — Question Generator (great before your next meeting)

⸻

Act as a program strategist preparing Tamar for a follow-up meeting.

Based on the meeting analysis below, generate:

• the 5 most important questions Tamar should ask next
• the 3 biggest risks that require clarification
• the 3 decisions that should be pushed toward resolution
• the 3 insights Tamar could contribute that would add strategic value to the discussion

Frame the questions in a way that demonstrates leadership, clarity, and operational awareness.

